and you'll make it.

16:17.541 --> 16:19.108
- Give us the truck.
- Josh, please...

16:19.152 --> 16:21.371
- Just shut up, Mom!
I know what I'm doing.

16:22.590 --> 16:24.679
We're taking the truck.

16:27.769 --> 16:30.119
- Do not ever turn on someone

16:30.163 --> 16:32.121
who just saved your ass.

16:32.165 --> 16:34.950
- Run.

16:34.994 --> 16:37.474
- Find a triage van.

16:37.518 --> 16:39.955
Go!

16:47.571 --> 16:51.706
- Purge and purify.
Purge and purify.

16:51.749 --> 16:53.925
Purge and purify.

