♪

16:59.322 --> 17:01.150
Lila?

17:01.194 --> 17:03.457
Lila, it's me.

17:03.500 --> 17:06.721
Lila.

17:06.764 --> 17:08.810
I know you can hear me.

17:08.853 --> 17:11.595
♪

17:11.639 --> 17:14.033
Look.

17:14.076 --> 17:16.818
What Rick said,

17:16.861 --> 17:19.647
it's not true.

17:19.690 --> 17:21.605
But none of that matters now.

17:22.998 --> 17:24.956
I think something's
about to happen.

17:25.000 --> 17:29.091
We need to get out of here.

17:29.135 --> 17:32.094
Open the door, Lila, please.

17:33.226 --> 17:34.923
- In for a penny,
in for a pound.

17:36.577 --> 17:39.232
It's a hell of a show
you're putting on here.

17:39.275 --> 17:42.713
- Where's that clever wife
of yours?

