- Uh, you know,
she needed to take a--

17:44.628 --> 17:46.717
a little-- I think a little
break from the excitement.

17:46.761 --> 17:48.850
- I like her.
Good.

17:48.893 --> 17:52.897
- She's got this verve
you need to watch out for.

17:52.941 --> 17:54.508
All right, well go tell her,

17:54.551 --> 17:57.467
"Stop being such a grouch
and come join the party."

17:57.511 --> 17:59.252
'Cause there are
a few more surprises

17:59.295 --> 18:00.644
you are not gonna want to miss.

18:00.688 --> 18:01.906
- Okay.

18:01.950 --> 18:03.386
And then you and me,
we still need to

18:03.430 --> 18:04.996
talk about you joining
the New Founding Fathers,

18:05.040 --> 18:07.782
because there are plenty
of other investors to meet.

18:07.825 --> 18:09.653
- Yeah, great.

18:09.697 --> 18:12.091
- To new partnerships.

18:12.134 --> 18:15.398
♪

18:15.442 --> 18:17.792
Go get her.
- Yeah.

18:17.835 --> 18:24.842
♪

18:34.461 --> 18:36.027
♪

18:38.900 --> 18:45.863
♪

18:45.907 --> 18:48.910
[indistinct announcements
over megaphone]

18:51.956 --> 18:53.915
- Give me your key card.

18:59.573 --> 19:01.270
Wait.

19:08.234 --> 19:11.324
This damn thing's been
acting up all night.

19:16.067 --> 19:19.332
Go on.
Leave your gun in the truck.

19:24.250 --> 19:25.512
You lying bitch!

19:29.080 --> 19:30.386
- Go! Go! Move!

19:30.430 --> 19:32.214
- Oh, God, oh!

19:36.349 --> 19:38.046
- We've got about 30 seconds
before he's back up.

19:38.089 --> 19:39.526
- You think you have the right

19:39.569 --> 19:41.223
to do whatever you want
tonight, huh?

19:41.267 --> 19:43.225
- It's the law!

19:43.269 --> 19:45.575
- Oh, my God.
- The Purge is not the law.

19:45.619 --> 19:47.751
It's the absence of law,
and when our government

19:47.795 --> 19:49.318
fails us, it's our mission
to protect those

19:49.362 --> 19:50.711
who can't protect themselves.

19:50.754 --> 19:53.888
- By any means necessary.

20:07.597 --> 20:09.904
- Nice haul, kid.

20:09.947 --> 20:12.036
Looks robust.

20:15.779 --> 20:17.303
For the auction.

20:17.346 --> 20:19.218
Have fun.

20:41.022 --> 20:43.807
I loved you so much.

20:43.851 --> 20:45.853
I was nothing without you,
Penny.

20:45.896 --> 20:50.640
I would have done anything
to keep you.

20:50.684 --> 20:51.772
And what do you do?

20:51.815 --> 20:53.904
You just--

20:53.948 --> 20:56.646
you just walk away.

20:56.690 --> 20:59.519
You walk away
and you never look back.

21:04.306 --> 21:06.352
- No, stop, come on, stop!
- Get away from me, Henry.

21:06.395 --> 21:08.484
- I just want
to talk to you, okay?

21:08.528 --> 21:10.834
Just stop, okay?

21:10.878 --> 21:13.272
- I love you so much.
Please.

21:13.315 --> 21:15.404
Please, I'll never--
I'll never do it again.

21:15.448 --> 21:17.580
- Please just get back...

21:17.624 --> 21:18.755
- Fuck you!

21:21.628 --> 21:22.716
Like, I love you, and
I don't want to do this to you!

21:22.759 --> 21:24.065
- No, Miguel!

21:24.108 --> 21:25.284
You're just gonna
make it worse!

21:32.552 --> 21:33.944
- Henry, stop!

21:33.988 --> 21:35.946
Stop it!

21:37.078 --> 21:38.993
Oh, fuck!
Oh, my God!

21:39.036 --> 21:43.171
Oh, my God! Oh, my God!

21:43.214 --> 21:44.955
- Stop, Miguel!
Stop!

21:46.435 --> 21:48.742
Stop, Miguel!
You're gonna kill him!

21:52.354 --> 21:54.008
- Look at him.

21:54.051 --> 21:55.575
You're gonna go to jail
for this.

22:07.108 --> 22:09.806
You betrayed me,

22:09.850 --> 22:12.766
you broke me,

22:12.809 --> 22:14.507
and then you left me.

22:14.550 --> 22:18.380
- You were already broken.

22:18.424 --> 22:19.773
I just didn't want
to wait around

22:19.816 --> 22:23.994
for you to fix it.

22:24.038 --> 22:26.649
I'm done being scared.

22:26.693 --> 22:28.912
I won't let you
hurt me anymore.

22:28.956 --> 22:31.132
You can't break me
because I am stronger

22:31.175 --> 22:33.743
than you are.

22:33.787 --> 22:37.443
All you can do is kill me.

22:37.486 --> 22:39.096
Everyone thinks this night

22:39.140 --> 22:41.708
will solve all their problems
but it can't.

22:41.751 --> 22:42.752
It won't.

22:42.796 --> 22:44.275
It doesn't solve anything.

22:44.319 --> 22:46.713
It just makes everything worse.

22:49.759 --> 22:51.674
♪

22:51.718 --> 22:55.809
So kill me.

22:55.852 --> 22:58.246
It's what you want, right?

22:58.289 --> 23:01.467
All your problems
will go away.

23:01.510 --> 23:03.599
Go ahead.

23:03.643 --> 23:07.298
[indistinct announcements
over megaphone]

23:07.342 --> 23:09.170
I surrender.

23:11.215 --> 23:13.392
♪

23:13.435 --> 23:17.657
But I'm not the victim.

23:17.700 --> 23:19.920
You are.

23:19.963 --> 23:26.970
♪

23:32.411 --> 23:35.196
- We just need to clean you up.

23:35.239 --> 23:36.676
- Oh, my God.

23:36.719 --> 23:38.634
- Madelyn,
you need to see this.

23:38.678 --> 23:41.289
- It's nothing, really.

23:41.332 --> 23:44.510
- Mm-hmm.
Right.

23:44.553 --> 23:46.816
It's always nothing.

23:46.860 --> 23:49.123
'Cause even when we're
the victims, we've been told

23:49.166 --> 23:51.560
to conceal and protect men.

23:51.604 --> 23:55.042
You're only enabling him when
you carry that shame alone.

23:55.085 --> 23:56.609
Let's get her out of here.

23:56.652 --> 23:58.480
- Wait,
where are you taking me?

23:58.524 --> 24:01.788
- Someplace safe
where he can't hurt you.

24:01.831 --> 24:03.398
- Come on, let's go.

24:03.442 --> 24:04.965
Come on.

24:05.008 --> 24:07.707
- Shut up!
- Thank you.

24:07.750 --> 24:09.839
I'll never
let you hurt me again.

24:11.275 --> 24:13.756
- And now the clean-up.

24:18.021 --> 24:19.806
Mm-mm!

24:19.849 --> 24:21.547
Mm-mm!

24:24.027 --> 24:26.552
- We don't enjoy this part,
but yeah.

24:26.595 --> 24:28.075
It's necessary.

24:28.118 --> 24:31.208
Once he's marked,
all women will know

24:31.252 --> 24:32.993
he's a violent animal.

24:33.036 --> 24:35.212
- And every time he looks
in the mirror,

24:35.256 --> 24:36.562
he'll remember tonight.

24:36.605 --> 24:38.128
- Oh--that doesn't
make it right.

24:38.172 --> 24:39.347
You don't need to do this.

24:39.390 --> 24:40.348
- You don't think
he deserves it.

24:40.391 --> 24:41.915
- No. Jesus.

24:41.958 --> 24:44.570
I'm saying that
there's a better way.

24:45.788 --> 24:47.486
A legal way.
- Oh, God.

24:47.529 --> 24:49.966
Laws change and evolve

24:50.010 --> 24:52.099
based on the whims of men.

24:52.142 --> 24:54.275
Sometimes we move
one step forward,

24:54.318 --> 24:55.842
sometimes three steps back.

24:55.885 --> 24:57.974
- We're ready.

24:58.018 --> 25:02.196
- Join us.

25:02.239 --> 25:05.112
- I couldn't live with myself.
No.

25:05.155 --> 25:06.896
- Funny, 'cause we sleep
better at night

25:06.940 --> 25:08.724
knowing who our enemies are.

25:08.768 --> 25:11.118
- Madelyn, I am telling you,
you're going to regret this.

25:11.161 --> 25:12.554
- Stop.
- You don't have--

25:12.598 --> 25:15.862
- If she misses,
we'll have to do it again.

25:15.905 --> 25:17.646
- Hold still.

25:17.690 --> 25:19.518
That's right, take it.

25:19.561 --> 25:20.519
Take it.

25:20.562 --> 25:22.346
- I'm leaving.

25:24.479 --> 25:31.486
♪

26:08.305 --> 26:14.442
♪

26:22.624 --> 26:23.886
Oh, shit...

26:25.975 --> 26:28.108
Okay, okay, okay...

26:34.375 --> 26:36.595
♪

26:38.205 --> 26:39.728
You know it's not safe
out there.

26:39.772 --> 26:42.252
- I have to go.

26:42.296 --> 26:46.387
I've done something terrible
and after everything I--

26:46.430 --> 26:48.737
I can't be responsible
for another person's death.

26:48.781 --> 26:51.174
I have to stop it.

26:53.916 --> 26:55.918
Then at least take this.

26:55.962 --> 26:58.573
Call the number,
we'll come marching in.

26:58.617 --> 27:01.054
- Thank you.

27:19.812 --> 27:21.074
- Move.

27:21.117 --> 27:23.293
Move!
- Hey, move over!

27:23.337 --> 27:25.556
- Hey!

27:25.600 --> 27:27.384
Hey!

27:27.428 --> 27:29.648
Hey! Hey!

27:29.691 --> 27:31.084
- Please, man!
- Hey!

27:31.127 --> 27:32.781
You've got the wrong guy!

27:32.825 --> 27:34.609
- Another word out of you
and you get the stick!

27:34.653 --> 27:36.263
- Listen to me, God damn it!

27:36.306 --> 27:37.786
- There's been a breach.

27:37.830 --> 27:39.483
- Oh, shit.
That's Rex.

27:39.527 --> 27:41.137
He's a collector!
Get him out of there!

27:41.181 --> 27:42.486
Move!

27:44.793 --> 27:47.230
- Let me out of here!
- Open up!

27:47.274 --> 27:49.102
- Help us!

27:49.145 --> 27:56.152
♪

28:06.075 --> 28:07.947
- Right this way!

28:07.990 --> 28:09.862
Show's about to begin!

28:24.746 --> 28:26.487
- Bring your weapons...

28:35.278 --> 28:36.627
- Dale.

28:40.849 --> 28:43.547
- I'm on leave.

28:43.591 --> 28:45.636
What the hell are you doing?

28:45.680 --> 28:49.597
- Purging one day a year keeps
me on point the other 364.

28:49.640 --> 28:50.990
Try it out, brother.

28:51.033 --> 28:53.079
- We're soldiers.

28:53.122 --> 28:55.168
We don't hurt civilians.

28:55.211 --> 28:57.213
No, this ain't for me, brother.

28:58.867 --> 29:00.782
- All right.

29:00.826 --> 29:04.830
♪

29:32.771 --> 29:34.555
- I can't talk right now, Ma.

29:34.598 --> 29:36.600
- The nurses said you called
while I was asleep.

29:36.644 --> 29:38.994
- It was nothing, Ma.
Go back to bed.

29:39.038 --> 29:41.649
- Now look, I know you didn't
call me to say nothing.

29:41.692 --> 29:44.608
Spit it out.
What's the matter?

29:44.652 --> 29:46.523
Jane, I don't have time
for this, baby.

29:46.567 --> 29:48.221
What's wrong?

29:48.264 --> 29:49.570
Um...

29:49.613 --> 29:51.920
Jane.

29:51.964 --> 29:55.097
- I'm sorry, Mom.

29:55.141 --> 29:58.492
I...

29:58.535 --> 30:02.017
just wanted to let you know...

30:04.498 --> 30:06.195
- I just wanted to let you know

30:06.239 --> 30:11.244
that no matter what happens--

30:11.287 --> 30:13.637
whatever happens...

30:13.681 --> 30:15.378
that I love you.

30:15.422 --> 30:17.206
- Baby.

30:17.250 --> 30:19.034
What's wrong?

30:19.078 --> 30:20.427
Jane.

30:35.790 --> 30:37.574
- Rick.

30:37.618 --> 30:38.880
Rick.

30:38.924 --> 30:40.577
Rick, listen to me.

30:40.621 --> 30:42.449
We need to leave.
We need to get out--

30:42.492 --> 30:45.452
- Shh.

30:45.495 --> 30:47.889
Do you hear that?

30:52.938 --> 30:55.070
Those gunshots
are really close.

30:55.114 --> 30:57.159
Come on.

30:57.203 --> 31:02.121
♪

31:05.776 --> 31:07.517
Oh, my God.

31:10.564 --> 31:13.088
♪

31:13.132 --> 31:14.394
It's fine, it's fine.

31:14.437 --> 31:15.525
The Stantons have
the best security--

31:15.569 --> 31:16.657
Holy shit.

31:18.789 --> 31:20.966
Lila, open the door!
- No, no! No, no, no.

31:21.009 --> 31:23.533
No, we need to hide, Jenna.
We need to hide.

31:23.577 --> 31:25.448
- The cellar.

31:25.492 --> 31:26.972
- You have to trust me.

31:27.015 --> 31:28.364
- Come on.

31:34.109 --> 31:36.590
- No, no, no, no.

32:05.053 --> 32:08.970
♪

32:11.190 --> 32:13.148
♪

32:13.192 --> 32:16.325
- ♪ Can you handle
the pressure? ♪

32:19.024 --> 32:20.808
♪

32:29.469 --> 32:37.216
♪

32:57.236 --> 33:04.243
♪

33:25.742 --> 33:28.963
It's me, Jane.

33:29.007 --> 33:31.096
- Safety compromised.

33:31.139 --> 33:34.142
Access the nearest
available panic room.

33:34.186 --> 33:35.448
- This way!

33:35.491 --> 33:37.058
- Safety compromised.

33:37.102 --> 33:38.929
Access the nearest
available panic room...

33:42.237 --> 33:45.284
- Go, go, go, go, go.

33:45.327 --> 33:47.329
Okay.
- We need to keep moving.

33:48.374 --> 33:49.897
Okay, okay.

33:49.940 --> 33:52.334
Which way
- Let's go this way.

33:52.378 --> 33:54.249
♪

33:54.293 --> 33:57.905
- There, there, there.

33:57.948 --> 33:59.254
Come on, come on!

33:59.298 --> 34:00.734
Come on!

34:00.777 --> 34:02.301
We need to go back.
We need to go back.

34:02.344 --> 34:04.390
We need--
- I wouldn't do that.

34:07.436 --> 34:10.831
♪

34:10.874 --> 34:12.963
- You're one of them.

34:13.007 --> 34:15.096
- Sometimes
revolution is the only way

34:15.140 --> 34:17.229
to make the world
a better place.

34:17.272 --> 34:18.839
- Please.

34:18.882 --> 34:21.407
We're not with them.
We're not NFFA.

34:22.756 --> 34:25.672
- I know.

34:33.158 --> 34:36.117
We have roadblocks
on Walnut and Spruce.

34:36.161 --> 34:38.206
Go across Franklin.

34:38.250 --> 34:40.208
You'll be safe
on the other side.

34:40.252 --> 34:42.123
- Thank you.

34:42.167 --> 34:44.256
- Lila...

34:44.299 --> 34:46.127
she's not one of them either.

34:46.171 --> 34:47.781
Please help her.
- Jenna, come on, baby.

34:47.824 --> 34:49.565
We gotta go.

34:49.609 --> 34:52.220
- No Stanton is safe tonight.

34:54.962 --> 34:56.268
- Come on.

35:12.980 --> 35:14.460
- Come with me!

35:14.503 --> 35:15.809
Let's get them!

35:15.852 --> 35:17.941
- Death to the NFFA!

35:17.985 --> 35:19.291
- Let's go!

35:19.334 --> 35:20.988
Get them!

35:21.031 --> 35:22.816
- Viva la revolution!

35:31.259 --> 35:33.870
♪

35:35.002 --> 35:36.569
- Purify my flesh.

35:36.612 --> 35:37.918
Prepare my soul.

35:37.961 --> 35:39.311
The Giving is here.

35:39.354 --> 35:41.226
The Invisible awaits.

35:41.269 --> 35:42.836
Purify my flesh.
- Shut up.

35:42.879 --> 35:44.577
Shut up! Shut up!
- Prepare my soul!

35:44.620 --> 35:46.013
The Giving is here!
- Shut up!

35:46.056 --> 35:47.188
- The Invisible awaits!
- Shut up!

35:47.232 --> 35:48.842
Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!

35:48.885 --> 35:50.583
- It's him!
Don't let him get away!

35:52.846 --> 35:54.848
- Grab him!

35:54.891 --> 35:58.199
- Penelope!
Penelope!

35:58.243 --> 35:59.766
- Penelope!

35:59.809 --> 36:01.420
Pen!

36:09.645 --> 36:12.866
- Penelope.

36:12.909 --> 36:15.564
- Yo.
He's mine.

36:15.608 --> 36:17.784
- Pay before play.
Carnival rules.

36:17.827 --> 36:19.351
- No!
No, let him go.

36:19.394 --> 36:21.527
It's me you want, Henry.

36:21.570 --> 36:24.747
- Yeah, no, I'll--
I'll pay whatever it takes.

36:27.010 --> 36:30.623
♪

36:30.666 --> 36:32.320
- Hey.

36:33.930 --> 36:36.019
- Group therapy begins
in five minutes.

36:39.240 --> 36:42.461
You were always tell me
to stop fighting,

36:42.504 --> 36:44.071
but now I'm getting paid
to do it.

36:49.381 --> 36:50.686
- Pen, I'm leaving.

36:50.730 --> 36:53.036
- I know.

36:54.168 --> 36:55.604
- I might not be coming back.

36:55.648 --> 36:57.693
- You knew.

36:57.737 --> 36:59.391
One more strike
and that would be it.

36:59.434 --> 37:02.524
They'd take you away
and I would be all alone.

37:02.568 --> 37:05.266
- You're not alone.
- I am now.

37:06.920 --> 37:11.098
- We can talk.
- Miguel, you're going to war.

37:11.141 --> 37:13.274
- I'll send you money
for your own place.

37:13.318 --> 37:14.841
I'll make this right,
I promise.

37:16.625 --> 37:18.801
By leaving?

37:18.845 --> 37:21.935
Or by never coming back?

37:21.978 --> 37:25.678
- I love you.

37:25.721 --> 37:27.854
I'll be back real soon, okay?

37:27.897 --> 37:34.687
♪

37:34.730 --> 37:37.733
I can't miss my bus.
- Just go.

37:46.829 --> 37:49.528
- Goodbye, Pen.

38:11.376 --> 38:13.726
Hi.

38:13.769 --> 38:16.772
Hi, my name is Tavis.
I'm a social worker.

38:16.816 --> 38:19.384
I'm here to talk to you
if you want.

38:19.427 --> 38:22.822
Was that your brother?

38:22.865 --> 38:25.825
I can tell.

38:25.868 --> 38:29.350
He loves you more
than anything in this world.

38:29.394 --> 38:33.354
And believe it or not,
he's in more pain than you are.

38:36.401 --> 38:39.752
♪

38:39.795 --> 38:41.623
Sometimes it's hard
to be strong

38:41.667 --> 38:45.018
for the people we love.

38:45.061 --> 38:47.455
And it's always the ones
we love the most

38:47.499 --> 38:52.286
who can break our hearts
the easiest.

39:00.120 --> 39:02.644
♪

39:04.429 --> 39:08.650
- If you see something,
do something.

39:08.694 --> 39:11.697
Because a storm is coming.

39:11.740 --> 39:17.137
♪

39:17.180 --> 39:20.706
When the rains come
and sink this rock,

39:20.749 --> 39:24.666
will you sink,
or will you swim?

39:26.059 --> 39:29.410
Drown or
fight your way to shore?

39:37.418 --> 39:39.942
What will you choose?

39:39.986 --> 39:42.771
I know what I think
you should do.

39:42.815 --> 39:44.643
Be a hero.

39:44.686 --> 39:47.210
Step up.
Put out that fire.

39:47.254 --> 39:49.430
Become the person tonight

39:49.474 --> 39:51.693
that you want to be tomorrow.

39:54.217 --> 39:57.830
- Hey, look!

39:57.873 --> 39:59.005
- Oh, you want...

40:02.400 --> 40:04.793
- Come on,
get over here, fat man!

40:07.840 --> 40:14.847
♪

40:23.159 --> 40:30.166
♪
